<P>THE GHOST. BOOK IV. BY C. CHURCHILL.</P>
<P>LONDON: Printed for J. COOTE, in Pater-no&s;ter-Row; W. FLEXNEY, at Gray's-Inn Gate, Holborn; G. KEARSLY, Ludgate-Street; T. HENDERSON, at the Royal-Exchange; J. GARDNER, in Charles-Street, We&s;tmin&s;ter; and J. ALMON, in Piccadilly. MDCCLXIII.</P>
