<L>Strutted, look'd big, and &s;wagger'd more</L>
<L>Than ever Hero did before,</L>
<L>Look'd up, Look'd down, Look'd all around,</L>
<L>Like MAVORS, grimly &s;mil'd and frown'd,</L>
<L>Seem'd Heav'n, and Earth, and Hell to call</L>
<L>To fight, that he might rout them all,</L>
<L>And per&s;onated Valour's &s;tyle</L>
