</LG>
<LG>
<L>WHIFFLE (who knows not WHIFFLE's name,</L>
<L>By the impartial voice of fame</L>
<L>Recorded fir&s;t, thro' all this land,</L>
<L>In Vanity's illu&s;trious band?)</L>
<L>Who, by all bounteous Nature meant</L>
<L>For offices of hardiment,</L>
<L>A modern HERCULES at lea&s;t,</L>
<L>To rid the world of each wild bea&s;t,</L>
<L>Of each wild bea&s;t which came in view,</L>
<L>Whether on four legs or on two,</L>
<L>Degenerate, delights to prove</L>
<L>His force on the <HI>Parade</HI> of Love,</L>
<L>Di&s;claims the joys which camps afford,</L>
<L>And for the Di&s;taff quits the &s;word;</L>
<L>Who fond of women would appear</L>
<L>To public eye, and public ear,</L>
