<L>She Jigg'd, and playing on the Flute,</L>
<L>Spread raptures o'er the &s;oul of BUTE.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Big with va&s;t hopes, &s;ome mighty plan,</L>
<L>Which wrought the bu&s;y &s;oul of man</L>
<L>To her full bent, the CIVIL LAW,</L>
<L>Fit <HI>Code</HI> to keep a world in awe,</L>
<L><PB N="157" REF="32">Bound o'er his brows, fair to behold,</L>
<L>As <HI>Jewi&s;h Frontlets</HI> were of old,</L>
<L>The famous CHARTER of our land,</L>
<L>Defac'd, and mangled in his hand;</L>
