</LG>
<LG>
<L>Next HART and DUKE, well worthy grace</L>
<L>And City favour, came in place.</L>
<L>No Children can their toils engage,</L>
<L>Their toils are turn'd to Rev'rend Age.</L>
<L>When a <HI>Court-Dame,</HI> to grace his brows</L>
<L>Re&s;olv'd, is wed to City Spou&s;e,</L>
<L>Their aid with <HI>Madam</HI>'s aid mu&s;t join</L>
<L>The aukward Dotard to refine,</L>
<L>And teach, whence true&s;t glory flows,</L>
<L><HI>Grave Sixty</HI> to turn out his toes.</L>
