<L>To &s;hew how fit he was to teach</L>
<L>A <HI>Cit,</HI> an <HI>Alderman,</HI> a <HI>Mayor,</HI></L>
<L>Led in a &s;tring a <HI>dancing Bear.</HI></L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Since the revival of <HI>Fingal,</HI></L>
