</LG>
<LG>
<L>On Hor&s;e, who proudly paw'd the ground,</L>
<L>And ca&s;t his fiery eyeballs round,</L>
<L>Snorting, and champing the rude bit,</L>
<L>As if, for warlike purpo&s;e fit,</L>
<L>His high and gen'rous blood di&s;dain'd</L>
<L>To be for &s;ports and pa&s;times rein'd,</L>
