<L>Horror be&s;trode a <HI>foreign</HI> bla&s;t,</L>
<L>And from the <HI>pri&s;on</HI> of the <HI>North,</HI></L>
<L>To FREEDOM deadly, Storms bur&s;t forth.</L>
